      "writtenOn": "2019-07-11T10:38:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I tried that and the semantics get a little weird. If the client creates a BackendTexture with a sampleCount of 1, how do we know to create the MSAA texture for it? It seems odd to set the BackendTexture\u0027s sampleCount to 4 when the native texture has a sampleCount of 1.",
      "parentUuid": "e39709b7_82f8de5c",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 105,
        "startChar": 33,
        "endLine": 105,
        "endChar": 69
      },
      "revId": "a7a1f122484cc0623a05e1a2c029cad54e440563",
